description: "Django templates & forms"
globs:
  - "templates/**/*.html"
alwaysApply: false
---

Templates:
- Use `{% url %}` and `{% static %}`; no hard‑coded domains.
- Avoid complex logic; push business rules into views/forms.
- Forms must include `{% csrf_token %}` and show server‑side errors.
- Directory pages: never render private fields unless the view explicitly provides them.